{"id":6234,"date":"2018-03-17T18:15:35","date_gmt":"2018-03-17T17:15:35","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/?p=6234"},"modified":"2022-04-08T10:11:00","modified_gmt":"2022-04-08T09:11:00","slug":"hpa-an-myanmar","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/myanmar\/hpa-an-myanmar\/","title":{"rendered":"Hpa-An, little hidden Treasure of Myanmar"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">8 Things to do in Hpa-An<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. Do a small hike up to Hpan Pu Mountain<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hpan Pu Mountain is the perfect way to experience Hpa-An. In this morning, take the canoe boat (500 kyats) from <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/GMwezTuPYfk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">this place<\/a>&#xA0;to the other side of the Thanlyin River. Expect to get a bit of dirt on your shoes. The people in this area they&#xA0;grow a lot of vegetables and sell them in Hpa-An.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155916\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-hike-Hpan-Pu-Mountain.jpg\" alt=\"things to do Hpa An myanmar hike Hpan Pu Mountain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"things to do Hpa An myanmar hike Hpan Pu Mountain\" class=\"wp-image-6398 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155916\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-hike-Hpan-Pu-Mountain.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155916\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-hike-Hpan-Pu-Mountain-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155916\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-hike-Hpan-Pu-Mountain-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\