roup\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Once you get off the boat, walk 350 meters until you reach a small town and note the sign to the left that says &#x2018;Hpan Pu Mountain&#x2019;. Once you are at the foot of the mountain, go right and walk around until <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/xc5jVvB9QM12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">this point<\/a>. On your left side, there is a stair that will lead you about 20 minutes to an amazing view over Hpa-An.<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6234&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155854\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-pin.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155854\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-pin-21x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155854\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-pin-414x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Hpa-An, little hidden Treasure of Myanmar\" height=\"600\" width=\"414\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Don&#x2019;t go up the mountain directly from the main road. You have to pass a temple so you have to leave your shoes behind while climbing to the top. Walk around the mountain (as mentioned above).<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-3 is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155914\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-hike-Hpan-Pu-Mountain-drone.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"338\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6400 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155914\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-hike-Hpan-Pu-Mountain-drone.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155914\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-hike-Hpan-Pu-Mountain-drone-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155914\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-hike-Hpan-Pu-Mountain-drone-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155914\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-hike-Hpan-Pu-Mountain-drone-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.sa