otels in Hpa-An<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-3 is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155951\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-boats.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6369 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155951\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-boats.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155951\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-boats-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155951\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-boats-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155951\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-boats-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155951\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-boats-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155951\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-boats-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155951\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-boats-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155951\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-boats-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155951\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-boats-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155951\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-boats-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155951\/th