hich makes it even more impressive. The entrance to the cave is 1000 kyat ($0.75) and a private boat ride about 3000 kyats. ($2.25)<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Good to know:<\/strong> This cave is closed during the rainy season.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-cave-drone.jpg\" alt=\"things to do Hpa An myanmar Saddar cave drone\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do Hpa An myanmar Saddar cave drone\" class=\"wp-image-6381 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155930\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-cave-drone.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155930\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-cave-drone-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155930\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-cave-drone-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155930\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-cave-drone-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155930\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-myanmar-Saddar-cave-drone-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155930\/things-to-do-Hpa-An-m